    public enum AcTerm
extends Enum<AcTerm>
implements Term, AlternativeNames
    All Audiovisual Core terms with namespace http://rs.tdwg.org/ac/terms/. See
    • http://rs.tdwg.org/ac/doc/termlist/2022-02-23 verison implemented here
    • https://ac.tdwg.org/termlist/
